quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  107,1,Beholdest thou him who belieth the Requital
  107,2,It is he who pusheth away the orphan
  107,3,And urgeth not the feeding of the poor
  107,4,"Woe, therefore, Unto such performers of prayer"
  107,5,As are of their prayer careless
  107,6,They who would be seen
  107,7,And who withholds even common necessaries